{"tid":1056444,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"背痛 膝頭痛 衝擊波治療","createTime":"2019-03-11T08:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T07:01:35.000Z","uid":144999,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0150e66286cc59256b4182716f25df61771d7c","tid":1056444,"uid":144999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:20:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過衝擊波治療？<br />\n<br />\n背痛左3年多了，中西醫都睇過唔少。之前有開post，可以去睇下。<br />\n<br />\n照過MRI, x-ray 都正常，應該係之前勞損或者整傷左，而自己又唔知，導致慢性嘅背肌筋膜發炎。<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過衝擊波個原理係先對發炎位置造成微少傷害，令大腦懂得重啟修復系統，去處理發炎位置。<br />\n<br />\n通常4-5次有好轉。我見有人就好啲，有人就覺得冇用。<br />\n<br />\n我想問下大家覺得有冇用，做左幾多次，去邊度睇，收費如何？ <br />\n<br />\n感謝大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e007cc6f3fe6b284362763eaaf6d8788d2b6fc90","tid":1056444,"uid":15344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:08:50.000Z","msg":"唔係剩係做shock wave就有效架 運動治療都係好重要"},{"pid":"eb51d39420eb45c17b7776007677c3a24f9141ce","tid":1056444,"uid":15344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"Btw 一般physio應該都有shock wave機做 收費600左近啦 唔係剩係做呢個機既"},{"pid":"7d366d82cbbadc5dd725b79306afe4c9296126f7","tid":1056444,"uid":75871,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:12:50.000Z","msg":"唔係治療師幫你整兩下就可以好返，需要配合運動來徹底根治"},{"pid":"10cfe599ed6b1ad0e7d8d97971e5c65605d25bab","tid":1056444,"uid":19660,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:22:04.000Z","msg":"個種酸同冤，係骨入面冤出黎<br />\n<br />\n難頂到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n退化性關節炎都放棄左咁滯<br />\n<br />\n睇左成皮野都唔見得會斷尾"},{"pid":"fec0f37a4f359fb06bfe85666d89638c1a32b4d2","tid":1056444,"uid":19660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:23:29.000Z","msg":"之前$580 <br />\n<br />\n衝擊波 上面講左好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n再4個吸盤吸吸下 電下 好舒服<br />\n<br />\n之後再開燈烘/曬下個膝頭"},{"pid":"308aceb7684d0933bd855bb8e34726f34db5c60b","tid":1056444,"uid":32832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"衝擊波開頂幾次係好痛<br />\n好似俾啲大針吉咁<br />\n但我嗰陣傷左去做衝擊波<br />\n要佢越開越大因為好痛得好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96218f0dfff33af30569c1a307415415d5eefed5","tid":1056444,"uid":19660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308aceb7684d0933bd855bb8e34726f34db5c60b","tid":1056444,"uid":32832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"衝擊波開頂幾次係好痛<br />\n好似俾啲大針吉咁<br />\n但我嗰陣傷左去做衝擊波<br />\n要佢越開越大因為好痛得好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:27:44.000Z","msg":"其實真係有用既，長期做<br />\n<br />\n因為我由開頭大半個圈既膝頭都冤痛<br />\n<br />\n去到後期得返1個凹位痛<br />\n<br />\n但已經claim爆左份保險停左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88244ec3a78179398b866ebbe7ec6cc99f514828","tid":1056444,"uid":211821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得針灸有效d, 不過大前提你要唔驚"},{"pid":"17b2e59b5f5d74c34fd76a7f00ff9440b92453e9","tid":1056444,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96218f0dfff33af30569c1a307415415d5eefed5","tid":1056444,"uid":19660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308aceb7684d0933bd855bb8e34726f34db5c60b","tid":1056444,"uid":32832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"衝擊波開頂幾次係好痛<br />\n好似俾啲大針吉咁<br />\n但我嗰陣傷左去做衝擊波<br />\n要佢越開越大因為好痛得好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:27:44.000Z","msg":"其實真係有用既，長期做<br />\n<br />\n因為我由開頭大半個圈既膝頭都冤痛<br />\n<br />\n去到後期得返1個凹位痛<br />\n<br />\n但已經claim爆左份保險停左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"我傷左幾次<br />\n次次都claim爆晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7f02ef6bd9784329c73f58a237b0c7bb73acde","tid":1056444,"uid":144999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88244ec3a78179398b866ebbe7ec6cc99f514828","tid":1056444,"uid":211821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得針灸有效d, 不過大前提你要唔驚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"其實我唔夾個背脊就唔痛嘅，但係正常夾唔會痛嘛⋯<br />\n<br />\n我而家針灸加推拿，醫師話可能要半年至一年先好... <br />\n<br />\n之前keep住做運動同拉筋，拉完係舒服啲，但轉頭又番黎，仲會更痛、更攰。<br />\n<br />\n而家個中醫師話唔好拉住，唔好成日諗痛，一覺得緊就拉腳，拉其他位置黎分散注意，哈，又真係冇咁攰喎！<br />\n<br />\n但我輕輕夾下背試下痛唔痛，又好似仲係咁痛......"},{"pid":"aa5b1cb8cb49f09dcd262a34e0b30f983c38859e","tid":1056444,"uid":144999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"我逢一、三、五去針同推拿嘅<br />\n<br />\n總之就係唔夾個背脊，就唔痛，但又好似唔係康復緊咁，好似只係逃避問題咁，大家明唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姐係病人同醫生講：醫生我隻手揸實拳頭會痛！<br />\n醫生：咁你唔好揸實<br />\n病人覺得：係喎！舒服啲喎！<br />\n<br />\n但其實係咪康復緊。。。"},{"pid":"81a92de112287bfd70c7b1810351b9d8c83542f0","tid":1056444,"uid":144999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb51d39420eb45c17b7776007677c3a24f9141ce","tid":1056444,"uid":15344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"Btw 一般physio應該都有shock wave機做 收費600左近啦 唔係剩係做呢個機既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"我唔郁會舒服啲，愈郁就愈攰愈痛，之前試過keep住做佢教個啲拉筋，話就話乳酸排掉就會唔痛，事實又唔係咁。。。"},{"pid":"47f05d1d7ecdb0241554b87ad2bee97c3b64efc2","tid":1056444,"uid":106959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eedeaff7740cfb7c19b780b8d259342715761c7d","tid":1056444,"uid":144999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f05d1d7ecdb0241554b87ad2bee97c3b64efc2","tid":1056444,"uid":1